Django REST API Docs
====================

Github
------

https://github.com/marcgibbons/django-rest-framework-docs

Pip installation
----------------

    $ pip install django-rest-framework-docs

Instructions
------------

Add "rest_framework_docs" to your INSTALLED_APPS setting like this:

    INSTALLED_APPS = (
        ...
        'rest_framework_docs',
    )

Paste the following into your URLconf

        url(r'^rest-api/', include('rest_framework_docs.urls')),

View /rest-api/ to see your Django Rest Framework endpoints
